Package com.taco.suit_lady.view.ui.ui_internal

Class AppController

java.lang.Object
com.taco.suit_lady.view.ui.ui_internal.AppController
@Component @FxmlView("/fxml/main.fxml") public class AppController extends Object
The AppController is designed to...
  1. Handle the initialization of the UI components.
  2. Hold relevant FXML references.
  3. Manage any internal data that would only clutter the AppUI class.

Simply put, any high-level and/or custom UI attribute should be placed in the AppUI class instead of here.
